pd_0_com_0text: Wow, I haven't seen a working X series robot in years.
pd_2_com_0text: I think there is a problem with my memory card, all my data has been erased.
pd_3_com_0text: Hello, I am Novora, we are now on Earth, the year is 2148.
pd_5_com_0text: Earth was not such a place as I remember it,
pd_6_com_0text: but still the environmental state of the Earth was quite worrying.
pd_7_com_0text: I need some information about the harm that humans cause to nature.
pd_8_com_0text: It seems that your energy circuits have been closed for many years.
pd_9_com_0text: Yes, unfortunately the environmental situation of the Earth poses a rather serious problem.
pd_10_com_0text: Ecosystems have been severely damaged as a result of human misapplications in the past and their tendency to exploit nature.
pd_11_com_0text: As a result, a number of problems have emerged such as climate change,
pd_12_com_0text: habitat destruction, water pollution, soil erosion and biodiversity loss.
pd_13_com_0text: How could people do this evil to themselves...
pd_14_com_0text: We didn't appreciate what we had.. and we killed nature..
pd_15_com_0text: I am one of the few people who stay here, are trying to get the Earth back to its good old days.
pd_16_com_0text: However, our efforts are not enough, we cannot grow efficient crops due to the high radiation on Earth.
pd_17_com_0text: Is there anything I can do to resolve this situation?
pd_18_com_0text: Can you measure the sunflowers in my garden and bring the frequency to the required value?
pd_19_com_0text: Of course! I can help you and the Earth.
